highlights.text: Tobias Sten has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “Fy faen du e deili” is the highest at #2.
“The Subway” by Chappell Roan is the highest new entry on Top Songs Norway at #15.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Norway the longest, at 351 days straight.
“Engel” by Admiral P and Nico D is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 58 spots at #97.
